title: FIN: A C.R. STECYK FILM AT H SPACE
description: We've recently joined forces with iconic artist C.R. Stecyk III on a special project in conjunction with his new short film "FIN" — set to debut on February 8 at the Hurley H Space Gallery at Hurley HQ. Peep the trailer, above. Also, keep an eye out for a series of limited edition tees from the project, dropping at a yet-to-be-determined date.
